al Engine 5 to deliver a smooth physics-based survival horror puzzle platformer under the guise of a unique pixel art style. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Under the hood, Solfall is able to utilize Unreal's <u>Lumen technology</u> to provide unique lighting conditions within this pixelized world. <br><br>Indirect lighting bounces from light sources to help you see what's lurking in the dark! <br><br></li><li>Enjoy a powerful physics engine powering movable obstructing and puzzle-based objects within the station. <br><br></li><li>Kinematics fuel the horrors that lay within deep space. <br><br></li><li>Full 360 degree camera and character motion allows for smooth perspective shifts navigating this top-down tale. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107210/extras/301606ad517cef9abe17c594f5b564b3.webp?t=1763618400\" width=600 height=32 /></span>",
